text: Ishparsovo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Podlesnensky Selsoviet, Sterlitamaksky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 767 as of 2010. There are 12 streets. == Geography == It is located 25 km from Sterlitamak, 3 km from Podlesnoye. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlitamaksky District
title: Ishparsovo
